text: Edith Jessie Thompson (25 December 1893 - 9 January 1923) and Frederick Edward Francis Bywaters (27 June 1902 - 9 January 1923) were a British couple executed for the murder of Thompson's husband Percy. Their case became a cause célèbre. Category:Murder in the United Kingdom Category:Executed English people
title: Edith Thompson and Frederick Bywaters
